      "Search, discover, and manage AI applications with built-in CLI commands for listing and filtering",
      "Track asynchronous task execution with status checking and result retrieval",
      "Automate Twitter/X operations including posting, direct messages, following, liking, and retweeting",
      "Generate sample inputs for any application and run with custom JSON parameters"
